channel.title: Can't connect to my no-ip
channel.description: Well, My server has been up and running 24/7 for the last week...and last night a crasher came on with a null bot system...and started crashing. So, i left it running with the auto-restarter on thinking he would go away sooner or later. Well, that was my mistake. I guess somehow he fucked my server stuff up. I just went and re-port-forwarded....And still, I can't connect. I can only connect with using 0.0.0.0, or 127.0.0.1 but those are my local connections only I can connect with. If someone could please help me, i would really appreciate it. Also, if your help is a success i'll make you a co on my server :) thanks, k0scape
